一位黄石餐饮老板的抗疫日记：退订3千桌团年饭，免费为医院送盒饭 | 深网。
An anti-epidemic diary by a Yellowstone restaurant owner: Resigned a 3,000-table reunion dinner and sent free cassettes to the hospital.
