作者 | 安然  编辑 | 康晓出品｜深网·腾讯小满工作室欢迎下载腾讯新闻APP，阅读更多优质资讯编者按：通过湖北各城普通民众的视角和抗疫行动，记录这一段难忘的历史。
Editing and Enron Editing & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
是为抗疫日记系列之三，来自黄石市烹饪酒店行业协会会长、三五轩饮食管理集团董事长曾文。
Is for the anti-epidemic diary series 3, from Huangshi City Cooking Hotel Industry Association President, Sanwu Futagami Catering Management Group Chairman Zeng Wen.
除夕那天晚上，一个医生朋友发了一个视频给我。
On New Year's Eve, a doctor friend sent me a video.
视频中一位医生在吃方便面，一位年轻的护士坐在旁边，哭的很厉害。
In the video, a doctor is eating instant noodles. A young nurse sits next to him and cries bitterly.
当时我看到视频后，特别难受。
When I saw the video, it was really hard.
作为抵抗疫情的一线医护人员除夕夜不能回家吃团圆饭不说，晚饭怎么能只吃方便面呢？当晚我就决定把三五轩准备做春节酒席的食材全部做成爱心盒饭，给有需要的医护人员送过去，最起码保证一线医护人员的吃饭问题。
As the front-line health care workers can not go home to eat reunion dinner on New Year's Eve, how can we just eat instant noodle for supper? That night I decided to make all the ingredients for the Spring Festival banquet into a love box for the medical staff in need, so as to ensure the food of the first-line medical staff.
早在农历29上午，我接到市里下发的要求餐饮企业退订酒席的通知。
As early as the 29th morning of the Lunar New Year, I received the notice issued by the city requiring catering enterprises to cancel banquet.
事实上在农历腊月26，三五轩就开始有顾客到店里排队退订酒席和押金，但其他餐饮企业还没有动起来，所以市场监督管理局和消协希望行业协会协助推动餐饮企业退订酒席。
In fact, on the 26th of the Lunar New Year, Futagami began to line up for redemption banquet and deposit, but other catering enterprises have not yet started to move, so the market supervision administration and the association hope that the industry association will help promote restaurant enterprises to withdraw.
图为顾客在三五轩饭店排队退押金接到通知后，我就在协会的微信群里下达通知，希望协会会员积极响应，并在全市的餐饮企业走访退订情况。
Pictured here is a customer queuing to return a deposit at San Futagami Hotel. After receiving the notice, I sent a message to the association's microphone group, hoping that the members would respond positively and that they would visit the restaurant business in the city to check the withdrawal.
其中有两家餐馆因为退订的事情与顾客发生了纠纷，被顾客投诉到了协会这里，后来经过协会协调，这些纠纷都解决了。
Two of the restaurants had a dispute with customers over the cancellation, which they filed with the association, and the dispute was settled after being coordinated by the association.
我们集团做过统计，截止年初三（27日），三五轩集团下属门店退订酒席3000多桌。
Our group has done statistics, as of the third day of the new year (27), 35 Xuan Group stores withdrew more than 3000 tables.
而协会初步统计，整个黄石市的餐饮行业已经陆续退订了3.6万桌酒席，退给消费者的押金近千万元。
The association preliminary statistics, the entire Huangshi City catering industry has been canceled 36,000 table banquet, the deposit returned to consumers nearly 10 million yuan.
初一起床第一件事，我就发布了一个“尽一份心！让一线医护人员吃上热饭！”的朋友圈，并留下了自己的联系方式，让黄石本地的医疗机构与我联系，为他们提供免费盒饭。
The first thing I got up at the beginning of my junior high school, I released a group of friends called "Do your part! Let the front-line staff eat hot rice!" and left my contact information so that Huang Shi's local medical institutions could contact me and provide them with free lunch boxes.
发完朋友圈后，我先给三五轩的几位厨师打电话，希望他们重回岗位为医护人员做饭，他们二话不说就赶回三五轩后厨，开始准备盒饭。
After sending out friends, I called several cooks in Futagami, hoping they would return to their posts to cook for the medical staff. Without saying a word, they rushed back to the hutch to prepare the lunch.
早上8:30左右，我又联系我们酒店的财务人员回来加班，给黄石市慈善总会捐了10万元，用于抗击新型冠状病毒疫情。
At around 8: 30 a.m., I contacted our hotel treasurer and returned to work overtime, donating $100, 000 to the Huangshi City Charity Association to fight the new coronavirus outbreak.
看到我们捐款后，很多餐饮企业都开始捐款。
After seeing our donation, many restaurants began to donate.
接近中午时，三五轩后厨就做好了480份盒饭，我们把运输车消毒后，将盒饭分别送达五医院、四医院、二医院、中医院、中医医院、中心医院的医生和护士手里。
Towards noon, the chef has made 480 boxes of rice. After disinfecting the trucks, we deliver the boxes to the doctors and nurses in five hospitals, four hospitals, two hospitals, Chinese medicine hospitals and central hospitals respectively.
一些医生拿到盒饭时，感动的哭了。
Some doctors were moved to tears when they got the boxed rice.
一位医生说，自己早上没吃早饭，还有一位护士说，自己早上就吃了一个馒头，一直撑到中午。
One doctor said he hadn't had breakfast in the morning, and another said he had eaten a steamed bun in the morning and stayed there until noon.
当时我们就跟医生们表态，三五轩安排了数名留守员工，以保证一线医护人员吃上热饭热菜，有需要直接给我打电话。
We told the doctors that Futagami had a few staff left behind to make sure the front-line staff could eat hot food and call me directly if necessary.
初二一大早，我就接到鱼头泡饭郭老板的电话。
Early in the morning of the second day, I received a fish head rice Guo boss telephone.
郭老板之前在三五轩饮食管理集团工作了十几年，后来自己出去创业，创办了鱼头泡饭。
Guo had been working for Futagami Food Management Group for more than a decade before going out on his own and starting his own fish head.
他在电话中说，听到三五轩在为医护人员免费送盒饭的消息，自己也想为医护人员做点事情。
He said by telephone that he wanted to do something for the medical staff when he heard that Futagami was giving free boxed meals to medical staff.
因为当天三五轩需要准备的盒饭量比较大，为了保证医护人员能按时吃上午饭和晚饭，我就把中午医院120份盒饭（中午60份，晚上60份）分给了鱼头泡饭。
Because Futagami needed to prepare a large number of boxed rice on the day, in order to ensure that medical staff can eat lunch and dinner on time, I will lunch hospital 120 boxes (60 at noon, 60 at night) to the fish head rice.
当时鱼头泡饭的厨师不够用，味道小镇的赵老板也积极加入，和鱼头泡饭一起完成了120份的盒饭。
At that time, there was not enough cooking fish head rice, taste the town's boss Zhao also actively joined, and fish head rice together with the completion of 120 boxed rice.
当天下午，黄石市内当地的楼上楼、楚乡厨艺、老邻居、金花大酒店等都开始跟我联系，希望加入给医院送爱心盒饭的行动中。
In the afternoon, the local buildings in Huangshi City upstairs, Chu Xiang cooking, old neighbors, Jinhua Hotel and so on began to contact me, hope to join the hospital to send love box rice action.
但是当天三五轩已经准备好了给各大医院的盒饭，最后决定后来加入的餐饮企业从初三开始给医护人员送餐。
But on that day, Futagami was ready to give the major hospitals boxed rice, finally decided to join the catering enterprises from the beginning of the third day of medical personnel to deliver meals.
当天，位于阳新的老兴国土豚汤和口味堂，看到三五轩在黄石市区的爱心送餐活动后，都开始联系阳新当地的医院，为当地医护人员提供爱心晚饭。
On the same day, located in Yangxin old Xingguo Dolphin Soup and Taste Hall, to see Sanwu Xuan in Huangshi District after the love delivery activities, they began to contact Yangxin local hospital, to provide a caring dinner for local medical staff.
由于给加入爱心送餐行动的餐饮企业越来越多，我初三早上就建了一个“协会为医院饮食服务”的微信群，统一调配各个医院的送餐服务。
Due to the increasing number of catering enterprises to join the action, I set up a "Association for Hospital Catering Service" micro-group on the morning of the third day of the unified deployment of hospital delivery services.
群里人员除了各大餐饮企业的负责人外，还有协会工作人员、配送员、一些医院保障科的工作人员等。
In addition to the heads of major catering enterprises in the group, but also Association staff, distribution staff, some hospital security section staff, etc.
初三的时候，三五轩之前储备的食材就已经不够用了。
At the beginning of the third, Futagami before the storage of food materials is not enough.
由于春节期间蔬菜供应紧张，我们盒饭加工成本持续上升，每个盒饭的价格在30元左右，每天免费盒饭的加工成本达2万余元。
Due to the shortage of vegetables during the Spring Festival, the cost of processing boxed rice continues to rise. The price of each box meal is around 30 yuan, and the cost of processing free boxed rice every day is over 20,000 yuan.
为了找到优质且平价的蔬菜，我们在初三找到了黄石润信农产品批发市场，看到我们免费给医院送餐后，他们承诺给我们供应平价食材，那里的大白菜每斤1.8元，红萝卜2元一斤，红菜苔3.5元一斤。
In order to find high-quality and affordable vegetables, we found Huang Shi Runxin Agricultural Wholesale Market in junior high school. After seeing us give free meals to the hospital, they promised to supply us with affordable ingredients.
图为黄石润信农产品批发市场蔬菜因为我们购买食材人员和运输人员需要一直在外面跑，我经常在群里强调，一定要带好口罩，做好防护。
Photo: Huang Shi Runxin Agricultural Wholesale Market Vegetables Because we need to buy ingredients staff and transport personnel to always run outside, I often stressed in the group, must wear masks, good protection.
几位医护人员了解情况后，特意送了运输人员几个N97口罩，嘱咐他们一定要注意安全，97口罩在医护人员那都很珍贵。
After several medical personnel to understand the situation, specially sent a few N97 masks to transport personnel, told them to be careful to be safe, 97 masks in the medical staff are precious.
初四那天，黄石越野协会的人联系到我，说希望加入爱心送餐行动中。
On the fourth day of junior high school, people from the Yellowstone Cross-Country Association contacted me and said they wanted to join in the love food service.
从这天起，各大医院中午和晚上的送餐都是由黄石越野协会的人负责了。
From that day on, lunch and evening meals at major hospitals were delivered by the Yellowstone Cross-Country Association.
昨天（27日），中医医院等一些医院发了接受爱心捐赠的公告，消毒用品和防护物资等都急缺。
Yesterday (27), the TCM Hospital and other hospitals issued a charitable donation announcement, disinfection supplies and protective materials are in urgent need.
看到这种情况我们就开始组织给医院购买消毒产品和防护物资。
Seeing this, we began to organize the purchase of disinfectant products and protective materials for the hospital.
前期我们从武汉的一个群里看到了有消毒水卖，就买了100瓶消毒水，货发过来后，我们送到医院，但医院反馈，这批消毒水不符合医院标准，没法用。
We saw disinfectant water from a group in Wuhan, bought 100 bottles of disinfectant water, the goods were sent to the hospital, but feedback from the hospital, the disinfectant did not meet hospital standards, can not be used.
我们只能把消毒水拿回酒店，自己拖地用了。
We had to take the disinfectant back to the hotel and mop the floor ourselves.
到初五，我们协会收到企业捐款总数马上30万了，我们准备全部用来买医疗物资，给中心医院、五医院、二医院、中医院等每个医院捐5万的物资。
By the fifth day of junior middle school, our association has received a total of 300,000 enterprise donations, we are ready to use all of them to buy medical supplies, the central hospital, the five hospitals, the second hospital, the Chinese hospital and other hospitals donated 50,000 materials.
但我们刚开始买到医用物资，都达不到医用标准，很多都是假的，买回来也不能用。
But we are just beginning to buy medical supplies, are not up to medical standards, many are false, buy back can not be used.
N95口罩、防护服这种医用物资不达标，很可能造成医护人员感染。
N95 mask, protective clothing this medical material is substandard, likely cause the medical staff to infect.
我们现在正在找有检验报告和符合国家标准的靠谱厂商，但还没找到合适的渠道和厂商。
We are now looking for testing reports and compliance with national standards of reliable manufacturers, but have not found the appropriate channels and manufacturers.
下午3:00多，之前给我们提供食材的老板，从大冶给我们运来了1千斤青菜和1千斤藕，但因为封路，到还地桥和铁山那就进不来了，有两辆大货车停在那里拦住了去路，我要想办法把这些菜运进来。
At 3: 00 p.m., the boss, who had previously provided us with ingredients, brought us 1,000 kilos of green vegetables and 1 kilo lotus root from Daye, but because of the road closures, it was impossible to get into the bridge and the iron mountain.
作者手记：与曾文的几次通话都是在他工作的间隙，10：00—14：30和16:00—18:30是“协会为医院饮食服务”的微信群最忙两个时间段，各大餐饮企业会在群里汇报给各大医院送餐的数量和接收的情况。
Author's Note: Several conversations with Zeng Wen took place between 10: 00-14: 30 and 16: 00-18: 30, the peak of the "Association for Hospital Catering Service" micro-groups, where major catering companies report on the number of meals delivered and received.
29号下午，曾文收到黄石爱康医院的感谢短信：“医院已经收到中餐，非常感谢。
On the afternoon of May 29, Zeng Wen received a thank-you note from Wong Shek Aikang Hospital.
但考虑到餐饮企业也有自身的难处，从明天起医院会安排食堂为医务人员提供工作餐，感谢这段时间的倾情帮助，大爱无疆！好人一生平安！”曾文说，感谢爱康医院的理解，但我们会尽全力将爱心送餐活动持续到疫情结束，为有需要的医院提供帮助。
But considering that catering enterprises have their own difficulties, from tomorrow the hospital will arrange canteens to provide working meals for medical staff. Thank you for all your help and love for Xinjiang! "Zeng said," Thanks to the understanding of Aikang Hospital, we will try our best to continue the feeding activities until the end of the epidemic.
电话最后，我问了一句，您自己也是餐饮企业老板，有没有考虑春节期间的损失。
Finally, I asked, you are also the owner of catering enterprises, whether the loss during the Spring Festival.
曾文停顿片刻说，“跟你说完全不考虑是假的，这个春节三五轩的损失就有300多万，还有房租、员工工资等固定开支。
Zeng Wen paused for a moment and said, "It's fake to tell you not to consider it at all. This Spring Festival lost more than three million yuan, plus fixed expenses such as rent and staff salaries.
不仅三五轩，从春节到正月十五，黄石整个餐饮行业损失预估肯定不小。
Not only Sanwu Xuan, from the Spring Festival to the fifteenth day of the first month, Huang Shi's entire catering industry losses are certainly not small.
但现在没有心思考虑经济损失的问题，黄石疫情及战斗在疫情最前线的医护人员工作环境才是黄石餐饮人最关心的事情。
But there is no concern about the economic loss, Yellowstone epidemic and the battle in the forefront of the health care workers working in the environment is the most concerned thing.
现在全国关注的焦点还是在武汉，像黄石等武汉周边地市的疫情大家关注度还不高，我们当地企业必须拧成一股绳，搏尽一份力”。
Now the national focus is still in Wuhan, such as yellow stone around the city of Wuhan's epidemic attention is not high, we have to join forces with local enterprises, to do their part.
